msgstr "Sjálfvirkt (byggt á eftirnafnshefð trésins)"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:23
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "Hegðun"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:23
msgid "Colors"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Colors the person boxes by family branch. Each couple shares the same color, "
"derived from the chosen base colors."
msgstr ""
"Litar persónurammana eftir fjölskyldugrein. Hvert par deilir sama lit, sem "
"er leiddur af völdu grunnlitunum."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Control panel"
msgstr "Stjórnborð"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:97
msgid ""
"Controls which name part shrinks first when a box is too narrow for the full "
"name. \"Automatic\" uses the tree's surname tradition (Icelandic abbreviates "
"surnames; everything else abbreviates given names)."
msgstr ""
"Stjórnar því hvaða nafnshluti er styttur fyrst þegar reitur er of þröngur "
"fyrir fullt nafn. „Sjálfvirkt“ notar eftirnafnshefð trésins (íslensk hefð "
"styttir eftirnöfn; aðrar stytta eiginnöfn)."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:23
msgid "Details"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Displays a person's alternate name, if available. This simultaneously "
"enlarges the individuals' respective boxes to create the necessary space for "
"the display."
msgstr ""
"Sýnir aukanafn einstaklings, ef það er til staðar. Þetta stækkar samtímis "
"kassa viðkomandi einstaklings til að skapa nauðsynlegt pláss fyrir skjáinn."

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/png-export-button.phtml:18
msgid "Export as PNG"
msgstr "Flytja út sem PNG"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/svg-export-button.phtml:18
msgid "Export as SVG"
msgstr "Flytja út sem SVG"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:50
msgid "General"
msgstr "Almennt"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/generations.phtml:22
msgid "Generations"
msgstr "Ættliðir"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/page.phtml:77
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "Fela fleiri valkosti"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:64
msgid "Hide the PNG export button"
msgstr "Fela PNG útflutningshnappinn"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:55
msgid "Hide the SVG export button"
msgstr "Fela SVG útflutningshnappinn"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/page.phtml:39
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Einstaklingur"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:46
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"Setur GEDCOM NICK-gildið innan gæsalappa milli skírnarnafna og ættarnafns "
"(t.d. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Líkir eftir gamla webtrees-hegðuninni fyrir "
"tré sem geyma gælunöfn í sérstaka GEDCOM NICK-reitinn."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:43
msgid "Maternal"
msgstr "Móður"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Modules"
msgstr "Einingar"

#: src/Module.php:272
msgid "Move the view with two fingers"
msgstr "Færðu yfirlitið með tveimur fingrum"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:86
msgid "Name abbreviation when space is tight"
msgstr "Nafnastytting þegar pláss er lítið"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:28
msgid "Open individual in new browser window/tab"
msgstr "Opnaðu einstakling í nýjum vafraglugga/flipa"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Open the current individual's detail page in a new browser window/tab when "
"it's left-clicked, otherwise the current window/tab is used."
msgstr ""
"Opnaðu upplýsingasíðu viðkomandi einstaklings í nýjum vafraglugga/flipa "
"þegar vinstrismellt er á hann, annars er núverandi gluggi/flipi notaður."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/orientation.phtml:22
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "Lega"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:39
msgid "Paternal"
msgstr "Föður"

#: src/Module.php:131 src/Module.php:252
msgid "Pedigree chart"
msgstr "Ættartölugraf"

